Non-turner on a good length, Rohit had already decided to play the reverse sweep, misses, the ball was close to both the toe-end of the bat and glove but it did not brush either, strikes Rohit in line and that's three reds. Commentary Text: Bumrah to W Saha, FOUR, Mumbai Indians review for an lbw against Saha! Looks like a very desperate review by MI, because this was clearly off the bat. A yorker length ball by Bumrah and Saha tries to squeeze it out, gets an inside edge that races past the leg-stump and it's away to the fine leg boundary in no time! Mumbai Indians have lost a review!
